: 50%; text-align: center; line-height: 32px; font-weight: bold; margin-right: 12px; vertical-align: top;\">3</div><div style=\"display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; width: calc(100% - 50px);\"><strong style=\"color: #1F2937; display: block; margin-bottom: 4px; font-size: 16px;\">Start Trading</strong><span style=\"color: #6B7280; font-size: 14px;\">Buy your first cryptocurrency</span></div></div></div><div style=\"text-align: center; margin: 32px 0;\"><a href=\"{{dashboardUrl}}\" class=\"button\">Get Started Now</a></div>"
